Class AbstractProcessController

    public abstract class AbstractProcessController
extends AbstractListenerManager<IProcessController.IProcessControllerListener,Object,Boolean>
implements IProcessController
    Help IProcessController implementations manage the listeners. Subclasses must arrange to call #notifyListeners(Object, Boolean) with the 1st argument ignored and the 2nd argument true if the listeners' startProcessing() methods are to be called, or false if stopProcessing().
